	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Level 31 is definately a bit rough to solo. I would wait until level 34. At your level the only things in OT that you can really solo are Sarnack Berzerkers and Tigresses. If a wandering monster comes by, like a tiger or cockatrice, you are dead.<br><br>I wouldn't do what another person suggested - fireshielding yourself. It is NOT a good idea to take hits at higher levels, and if you never have to tank for your pet, then you just wasted mana fire-shielding yourself.<br><br>At your level I would try soloing Dwarfs and Sisters in OOT. They can easily get you to level 34, at which point you can go back to OT.<br><br>Former EQ Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
