	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;  Pet immunities.  Very simple.  Fire resists fire, water resists poison, air resists cold, earth resists disease.  They all have crappy resists vs magic (the epic has all-around decent resists vs everything, but no immunities).<br><br>    All of this has been tested.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
