	   <tr><td colspan=2>Um, the diety you pick doesn't have any impact on how powerful your magician is. Pick the diety that you feel your character would be best at worshipping, or at least believing in. The diety you pick should be what you want your character to *GASP* roleplay. The diety you pick also has an impact on your faction, but it really doesn't matter. Seriouslly just choose the diety that you like the most by the description.<br><br>Former EQ Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
