	   <tr><td colspan=2>The earth pet has the most hitpoints out of all of the pets, so you want to use him for fights against harder monsters. The root is useful when fighting things that agro easily, or things that run away at quick speeds. If you want quick kills though, use the fire pet. If you are unsure of which pet to use, go with water. Air isn't as useful at your level as at the later levels. It will become a very good pet though, so just you wait.<br><br>Former EQ Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
